title: For Sale:  AIMS-74 - Unfired, brand new build
postcontent:
This is a brand new build from Atlantic Firearms using a recently imported Romanian AIMS-74 parts kit.  These were unheard of in the states until a few years ago.  This is side folding AK-74 variant chambered in 5.45x39 and is a beautiful build using enough USA parts to make it 922R compliant.  I bought it and realized that I have other kits to build and this will just go unused in my safe.The barrel is a US-made nitrided barrel along with a US-made receiver, Tapco G2 FCG, and an Atlantic Firearms US-made bakelite grip.  The original AIMS-74 bakelite grip is included along with the AIMS-74 cleaning rod.  The furniture is gorgeous and my guess is that this was a CAT 1 build kit (basically unfired before demilling).  The only number not matching is the top cover.  The side folding wire stock is offset for right-handed shooters and is comfortable if you're a right-handed shooter.  I am left-eye dominant, so it's another reason why I am selling.  
The sling is NOT included.  The Atlantic Firearms soft-padded case, (1) Romanian 5.45x39 magazine, and the rifle is all included in the sale.  This will be a sweet-shooter for the next owner.  I never fired it, so it has only been test fired by Atlantic.  The action is very smooth with no binding as is the safety and the sights are straight.  Atlantic did a terrific job with this rifle.  This is a very unique variant of the AK-74.
I can ship, but it will cost extra and take a little more time.  FTF with cash is preferred and the buyer will sign a bill of sale along with provide an ID and LTCH.  I will only ship to an FFL.
